title: Counter Strike 1.6 Windows 8 fully compatible
description:
Clean version of infamous game Counter-Strike 1.6

This version is completely compatible with Windows 8.

The game has all possible security installed.

The game cariies clean config and Steam models.

It is 100% ads free and protected from any ad binds and other harmful server cmds.

The game is immune to amx_destroy plugin (which messes up player's client).

The game supports 48 protocol.

The performance is very smooth and lags free.

You can find some best servers in "Find servers" option (top servers from gametracker.com).
